```{r pancreas 32740256, include=FALSE}

PMID_32740256 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32740256', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32740256 <- paste0(PMID_32740256$journal,' ', PMID_32740256$year, ' ', PMID_32740256$month,';', PMID_32740256$volume,'(', PMID_32740256$number,'):', PMID_32740256$pages)

PubMed_32740256 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32740256$eprint)

doi_32740256 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32740256$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
